snippet.title: Teaser Project Andalas : Realms Of Eternal Lights
snippet.description:
Help us by Wishlist us on steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3367720/ANDALAS__Realms_of_Eternal_Lights/

Join Rei, a brave boy battling brain cancer, on a quest to save the enchanting land of Andalas. Customize your adventure by using tools and items to defeat monsters, transform into powerful ancient figures, and summon Companion pets. Collect relics to uncover secrets and rescue Andalas!

Discord : https://discord.gg/wftPySQfnR
Instagram : https://instagram.com/busybeaverstudio
X : https://x.com/BusyBeaver_s
